caption.title: Bayes factor (BF) rates of epidemiological links between Caribbean and Brazilian locations for dispersal of non-pandemic BCAR lineages.
caption.p: BF > 100 indicates decisive support, 30 ≤ BF ≤ 100 indicates very strong support, 10 ≤ BF ≤ 30 indicates strong support, and 6 ≤ BF ≤ 10 indicates substantial support for migration between locations.
